  <description>
    <p>This is an unofficial Flatpak version of Friday Night Funkin'. I am unaffiliated with the Funkin' Crew Inc.</p>
    <p>yo! really think so?</p>
    <p>What is there even in this game?</p>
    <ul>
      <li>8 main weeks</li>
      <li>Erect Remixes for most songs</li>
      <li>Pico Mixes for some songs</li>
      <li>Funky graphics</li>
    </ul>
